<tbody>
<tr class="even firstrow"><td colspan="2"><span class="courselistcomment">Select from a list of courses within the School of Public Health and across campus representing an array of bench, lab, and applied sciences. Students are highly encouraged to consider <a href="/search/?P=PUBH%20393" title="PUBH 393" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PUBH 393');">PUBH 393</a> for one of their selective options. <a href="/search/?P=PUBH%20420" title="PUBH 420" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PUBH 420');">PUBH 420</a> is among the selective options and may be a prerequisite requirement for some other public health courses on the list. </span></td><td class="hourscol">15</td></tr>
<tr class="odd"><td colspan="2"><span class="courselistcomment">Select elective courses preapproved by the advisor as relevant to the student's plan of study.</span></td><td class="hourscol">3</td></tr>
<tr class="even lastrow"><td colspan="2"><span class="courselistcomment">Additional free electives</span> <sup>a</sup></td><td class="hourscol">7</td></tr>
<tr class="listsum"><td colspan="2">Total Hours</td><td class="hourscol">25</td></tr></tbody>
</table>

